## Mathematical Background

### Forward Pass

```
z1 = X · W1 + b1
a1 = sigmoid(z1)

z2 = a1 · W2 + b2
a2 = sigmoid(z2)
```

### Backward Pass

```
dL/dz2 = (a2 - y) * sigmoid_derivative(z2)
dW2 = a1^T · dL/dz2 / m
db2 = sum(dL/dz2) / m

dL/dz1 = (dL/dz2 · W2^T) * sigmoid_derivative(z1)
dW1 = X^T · dL/dz1 / m
db1 = sum(dL/dz1) / m

W = W - lr * dW
b = b - lr * db
```

